Well, this is my first map.

If you start in the small room there should be a red or blue light in your spawn.
(Red for terriost)
(Blue for CT's)

When you go through the teleport it takes you to a sort of aim map.

There is one trap in the map.

Three secret rooms. (Two rooms have my friends initials and one is a gun room.)

Please comment and tell me what I need to add to this map.


Thanks.

PLEASE COMMENT!
I'll post some new screenshots some other time.
